reviewText:
This show takes a fun, somewhat educational, slightly irreverent look at southern Vermont. If you live here you are bound to recognize people you know on the show because the guests are the residents and visitors of Brattleboro.

Someone told me she watched Naked Brattleboro when she was doing online research about the area and then she ultimately decided to move to Brattleboro partly because she saw the show and thought Brattleboro would be a fun and friendly place to live.
